seo: 帆软FineReport,任意文件覆盖漏洞,漏洞检测,安全测试
summary: 该插件用于检测帆软FineReport V9系统是否存在任意文件覆盖漏洞，通过发送特定的HTTP请求来验证漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the FineReport V9 system has arbitrary file overwrite vulnerabilities, and verifies the existence of vulnerabilities by sending specific HTTP requests.
